	<h3>Hide</h3> 
<p><strong>If you can’t leave, hide.</strong></p> 
<p>Hide with as many others as you safely can. Get behind solid structures that can't be penetrated by weapons or weapon fire. Lock, barricade and stay away from the door. Close windows, blinds and turn off lights. Stay quiet and mute phones. Wait until help arrives.</p>
