<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="05e953d7-b56c-4b4c-ad1e-c6d7b489f010" >

    <p>An active attacker may:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>display a weapon (e.g. firearm, knife, etc.)</li> 
 <li>actively engage in threatening conduct or behaviour</li> 
 <li>show no reasoning behind their selection of victims</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#05e953d7-b56c-4b4c-ad1e-c6d7b489f010");});</script></div>

