<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="3824ed46-934d-4bd0-b4c7-53e1db42f003" >

    <p>An active threat may:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>begin without warning</li> 
 <li>cause confusion and panic</li> 
 <li>result in people having a ‘freeze’ response</li> 
 <li>involve firearms or knives</li> 
 <li>involve explosive devices to cause additional harm and to impede response</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
